<doc>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS">
    <summary>
      <para>Defines the possible states of <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/directmanipulation/direct-manipulation-portal">Direct Manipulation</a>. The viewport can process input in any state unless otherwise noted.</para>
    </summary>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/directmanipulation/direct-manipulation-enumerations">Direct Manipulation Enumerations</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_BUILDING">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport is being initialized and is not yet able to process input.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_ENABLED">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport was successfully enabled.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_DISABLED">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport is disabled and cannot process input or callbacks. The viewport can be enabled by calling <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/api/directmanipulation/nf-directmanipulation-idirectmanipulationviewport-enable">Enable</a>.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_RUNNING">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport is currently processing input and updating content.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_INERTIA">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport is moving content due to inertia.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_READY">
    <summary>
      <para>The viewport has completed the previous interaction.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="DIRECTMANIPULATION_STATUS.DIRECTMANIPULATION_SUSPENDED">
    <summary>
      <para>The transient state of the viewport when input has been promoted to an ancestor in the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//previous-versions/windows/desktop/api/directmanipulation/nf-directmanipulation-idirectmanipulationviewport-setcontact">SetContact</a> chain.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>